Subject: [PATCH] KVM: PPC: Book3S HV: Skip kvmppc_uvmem_free if Ultravisor is
 not supported
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.6.5
Git-commit: 9bee484b280a059c1faa10ae174af4f4af02c805

commit 9bee484b280a059c1faa10ae174af4f4af02c805 upstream.

